title: Grateful Dead Live at Golden Hall, Community Concourse on 1978-01-08
lineage: MAC >> Nakamichi CR7a => Korg MR-1000 >> DSF [1-bit 5.6448 MHz Stereo] >>  Korg AudioGate >> WAV [24/96]
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Mama Tried-> Big River, Sunrise, It's All Over Now, Looks Like Rain, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Good Lovin', Estimated Prophet-> Drums-> The Other One-> Truckin'-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Johnny B. Goode
